The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Advani website
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Advani website
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: Sportz Interactive on Wednesday, launched pankajadvani.com  the official website for world champion Pankaj Advani.         
	Advani, also the reigning national and Asian champion said: The web is an effective medium of communicating with the world at large. I believe a platform like Sportz People gives a sportsperson direct access to his fans and also makes him approachable.                                                                                                                          
